haiku:
Golden sunset fades


Ripples on the quiet lake


Summer's gentle peace

Snowflakes gently fall
Blanketing the winter scene
Frosty morning calm

Soft wind whispers low,
Cherry blossoms dance and fall,
Spring's gentle embrace.

Golden sunset fades


Ripples on the quiet lake


Summer's gentle kiss

Snowflakes gently fall
Blanketing the winter scene
Frosty morning calm

Winter's icy breath
Paints the window with frost art
Silence fills the air

Snowflakes gently fall
Blanketing the winter scene
Frosty peaceful hush

Golden sunset fades
Ripples on the quiet lake
Summer's gentle night

Wind whispers through trees
Leaves dance in a golden shower
Autumn's gentle touch.

Snowflakes gently fall
Blanketing the winter scene
Frosty peaceful hush

Snowflakes gently fall
Blanketing the winter scene
Frosty morning dawns

Soft wind whispers low
Through leaves of crimson, gold, brown
Autumn's gentle touch.

Soft petals unfurl
Dancing in the warm breeze sweet
Morning's gentle kiss

Moonlight on the sea
Waves caress the sandy shore
Midnight's gentle song

Cherry blossoms bloom

Pink snow falls on ancient ground

Spring's sweet breath arrives

Moonlit city streets
Rainy night's symphony
Urban heartbeat sounds

Moonlit forest dark
Shadows hide the ancient trees
Midnight's silent hush

Cool autumn wind blows
Leaves of red and gold descend
Earth breathes a deep sigh
